basics.name: Jane Doe
basics.label: Front End Web Developer
basics.summary: Senior backend software engineer with 10+ years of experiences in developing various applications for different platforms, incorporated into all all phases of the software development cycle transitioned into Frontend Web Development after a career pause. Hard working, flexible, reliable and responsible professional who maintains positive relationships with team members. Learning all the time, willing for continual professional development.
